"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:5.5\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">5.5</span> 標題：床、褥子（bed, sleeping mat）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： יָצוּעַ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： yatsu‘a)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:4\">GEN 49:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr5:1\">1CH 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job17:13\">JOB 17:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:7\">PSA 63:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:3\">PSA 132:3</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מִטָּה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： mitah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:31\">GEN 47:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:2\">GEN 48:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:33\">GEN 49:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:28\">EXO 7:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:13\">1SA 19:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:15\">1SA 19:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:16\">1SA 19:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:23\">1SA 28:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam4:7\">2SA 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:19\">1KI 17:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:4\">1KI 21:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:4\">2KI 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:6\">2KI 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:16\">2KI 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:10\">2KI 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:21\">2KI 4:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:32\">2KI 4:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs11:2\">2KI 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr22:11\">2CH 22:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:25\">2CH 24:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:6\">EST 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth7:8\">EST 7:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:7\">PSA 6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:14\">PRO 26:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song3:7\">SNG 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:41\">EZK 23:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:12\">AMO 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos6:4\">AMO 6:4</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מֵסַב</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： mesav)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:12\">SNG 1:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מַצָּע</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： matsa‘)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:20\">ISA 28:20</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מִשְׁכָּב</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： mishkav)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:4\">GEN 49:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:28\">EXO 7:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:18\">EXO 21:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:4\">LEV 15:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:5\">LEV 15:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:21\">LEV 15:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:23\">LEV 15:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:24\">LEV 15:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:26\">LEV 15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:26\">LEV 15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:22\">LEV 18:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:13\">LEV 20:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:17\">NUM 31:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:18\">NUM 31:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:35\">NUM 31:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg21:11\">JDG 21:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg21:12\">JDG 21:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam4:5\">2SA 4:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam4:7\">2SA 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam4:11\">2SA 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:2\">2SA 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:13\">2SA 11:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:5\">2SA 13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:28\">2SA 17:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:47\">1KI 1:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:12\">2KI 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:14\">2CH 16:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:13\">JOB 7:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:15\">JOB 33:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:19\">JOB 33:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:5\">PSA 4:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:5\">PSA 36:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:4\">PSA 41:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:5\">PSA 149:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:17\">PRO 7:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:27\">PRO 22:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:20\">ECC 10:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song3:1\">SNG 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:2\">ISA 57:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:7\">ISA 57:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:8\">ISA 57:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:8\">ISA 57:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:17\">EZK 23:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek32:25\">EZK 32:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos7:14\">HOS 7:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:1\">MIC 2:1</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： עֶרֶשׂ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ‘eres)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut3:11\">DEU 3:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut3:11\">DEU 3:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:13\">JOB 7:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:7\">PSA 6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:4\">PSA 41:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:3\">PSA 132:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:16\">PRO 7:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:16\">SNG 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:12\">AMO 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos6:4\">AMO 6:4</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： κλινάριον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： klinarion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:15\">ACT 5:15</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： κλίνη</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： klinē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:2\">MAT 9:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:6\">MAT 9:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:21\">MRK 4:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:4\">MRK 7:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:30\">MRK 7:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:18\">LUK 5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:16\">LUK 8:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:34\">LUK 17:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:22\">REV 2:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Tob8:4\">TOB 8:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Tob14:11\">TOB 14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt8:3\">JDT 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt10:21\">JDT 10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt13:2\">JDT 13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt13:4\">JDT 13:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt13:6\">JDT 13:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt13:7\">JDT 13:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt15:11\">JDT 15:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EsthGr1:6\">ESG 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EsthGr7:8\">ESG 7:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir23:18\">SIR 23:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir48:6\">SIR 48:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： κλινίδιον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： klinidion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:19\">LUK 5:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:24\">LUK 5:24</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： κοίτη</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： koitē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:7\">LUK 11:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:10\">ROM 9:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:13\">ROM 13:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:4\">HEB 13:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt13:1\">JDT 13:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/EsthGr4:17\">ESG 4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis3:13\">WIS 3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis3:16\">WIS 3:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir31:19\">SIR 31:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir40:5\">SIR 40:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir41:24\">SIR 41:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc1:5\">1MA 1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc6:8\">1MA 6:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/PssSol17:16\">PSS 17:16</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： κράβαττος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： krabattos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:4\">MRK 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:9\">MRK 2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:11\">MRK 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:12\">MRK 2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:55\">MRK 6:55</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:8\">JHN 5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:9\">JHN 5:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:10\">JHN 5:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:11\">JHN 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:15\">ACT 5:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:33\">ACT 9:33</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： στρωμνή</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： strōmnē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt9:3\">JDT 9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt13:9\">JDT 13:9</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： φορεῖον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： foreion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc3:27\">2MA 3:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc9:8\">2MA 9:8</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Latin</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">拉： cubile</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Esd3:1\">2ES 3:1</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Latin</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">拉： lectus</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Esd12:26\">2ES 12:26</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/OAI-0045_sleeping_mat.png\" alt=\"OAI-0045_sleeping_mat\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\"> (Image generated by ChatGPT using OpenAI technology)</figcaption></figure>床是供人睡覺的物品。在某些情況下，床可能是一個架高的家具。然而，迦南的閃族人通常不睡在架高的床上，而是睡在鋪在地上的獸皮上。架高床的形狀與現今大多數文化中使用的床相似：是一個用四條腿支撐起來的低矮平面，比人稍高，寬約70—80厘米（27—31英吋）。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/PTZ-0083_wooden_bed.jpg\" alt=\"仿制的木床\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">仿制的木床 (© Ray Pritz by United Bible Societies)</figcaption></figure>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:31\">GEN 47:31</a> ：古埃及人——尤其是富人——使用的床與今天大多數文化中的床非常相似。這種床已經在埃及的多座墳墓中出土。埃及人有時會用頭枕來代替枕頭。這些頭枕是木頭做的，略微凹陷，底座高20厘米（8英吋）或以上。雅各可能就是屈身在這種頭枕（比較<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> 的“pillow”「枕頭」）上面。翻譯這節經文時，也可以考慮另一種可能性。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 將希伯來文<em>mitah</em> 譯為“bed”（「床」），但這個詞也可以指「杖」，《七十士譯本》就是這樣理解的（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:21\">HEB 11:21</a> 和<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 也採取這種解釋）。然而，絕大多數譯本都譯為「床」。翻譯者不必統一本節經文和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:21\">HEB 11:21</a> 的譯法。</p>\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/UBS-0030_bed.jpg\" alt=\"用不同材料製作的床\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">用不同材料製作的床 (© Deutsche Bibelgesellschaft, Stuttgart by United Bible Societies)</figcaption></figure>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:7\">PSA 6:7</a> （《和》6:6）：這節經文的第三行「我的長榻」（“My couch”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）和第二行「我的床」同義。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> （<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> 同）使用了更為自然的當代對等詞“bed”（「床」）和“pillow”（「枕頭」）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:12\">SNG 1:12</a> ：希伯來文<em>mesav</em> 僅出現在此處，指一件家具。大多數現代譯本都將其理解為一種「長榻」（“couch”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ），但有些譯本認為它指的是人們斜躺著就餐的矮「桌子」（“table”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"King James Version (1611)\">KJV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New American Standard Bible\">NASB</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Spanish Common Language Version (Dios Habla Hoy)\">SPCL</abbr> ）。一些譯本把經文的第一行譯為，「我王在我旁邊的時候」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"German Common Language Version (Gute Nachricht Bibel)\">GECL</abbr> 直譯），或「我王在他的筵席中」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"French Common Language Version (Bible en français courant)\">FRCL</abbr> 直譯），避免了指明是什麽家具的問題。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Traduction Oecuménique de la Bible (French, 1975)\">TOB</abbr> 把<em>mesav</em> 譯為“enclosure”（「圍繞」），並在腳註中解釋說：雖然這個詞可能指圍繞餐桌的床或圍繞這對夫婦的朝臣，但它在這裡說的是一個花園，其中的香氣吸引了王。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Italian Common Language Version\">ITCL</abbr> 採取了這種解釋，譯文第一行的意思是：「現在我的王在他的花園裡。」</p>\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/OAI-0010_rollingup_mat.png\" alt=\"男人捲起他的墊子\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">男人捲起他的墊子 (Image generated by ChatGPT using OpenAI technology)</figcaption></figure>在新約的一些經文中，希臘文<em>klinarion</em> 、<em>klinidion</em> 和<em>krabattos</em> 指的是折疊床或擔架，病人或康復中的人可以躺在上面休息或轉移。這種折疊床或擔架可能是用蘆葦或布做的，又輕又薄，一個人就可以輕鬆地把它捲起來或折疊起來帶走。在提到這些詞語的新約經文中，沒有一處指的是人們斜躺在上面吃飯的長榻。</p>\n<p>希臘文<em>klinē</em> 通常泛指任何用來斜靠或躺臥的家具。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:2\">MAT 9:2</a> 中，「擔架」或「折疊床」等譯法顯然比傳統的「床」（“bed”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）更為可取，因為「床」可能暗示這是一件很大的家具。翻譯者每次翻譯<em>klinē</em> 一詞時，都應選用最符合上下文的物件類型。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:7\">LUK 11:7</a> ：對於「我的孩子們也同我在床上了」（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）這句話，不必認為這人和他的孩子們是在同一張床上；當然，這裡所指也可能是一個相對簡陋的房子，全家人都睡在房間某個角落的地板上，或者一個架高的平臺上。這段經文可以簡單地譯為：「我已經上床睡覺了，我的孩子們也是」，或「我已經在床上了，我的孩子們也是」。</p>\n<p>床有時用作比喻。在一些經文中，床指的是婚內或婚外的性行為（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:13\">ROM 13:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis3:13\">WIS 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis3:16\">WIS 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir23:18\">SIR 23:18</a> ）。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:10\">ROM 9:10</a> 中，希臘文<em>koitē</em> 和動詞<em>echō</em> 一起使用，意思是「懷孕」。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc1:5\">1MA 1:5</a> 中，文本的字面意思是亞歷山大「倒在床上」，意即他「生病了」（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
